name: ndarray.T
description: Returns a copy of the array with axes transposed.

name: ndarray.as_in_context
description: Returns an array on the target device with the same value as this array.

name: ndarray.as_nd_ndarray
description: A convenience function for creating a classic ndarray from the current ndarray with zero copy. For this class\, it just returns itself since it is already a classic ndarray.

name: ndarray.asnumpy
description: Returns a numpy.ndarray object with value copied from this array.

name: ndarray.asscalar
description: Returns a scalar whose value is copied from this array.

name: ndarray.astype
description: Returns a copy of the array after casting to a specified type.

name: ndarray.attach_grad
description: Attach a gradient buffer to this NDArray\, so that backward can compute gradient with respect to it.

name: ndarray.backward
description: Compute the gradients of this NDArray w.r.t variables.

name: ndarray.broadcast_like
description: Broadcasts the input array to the shape of other.

name: ndarray.broadcast_to
description: Broadcasts the input array to a new shape.

name: ndarray.copy
description: Makes a copy of this NDArray\, keeping the same context.

name: ndarray.copyto
description: Copies the value of this array to another array.

name: ndarray.ctx
description: Device context of the array. Has the same meaning as context.

name: ndarray.detach
description: Returns a new NDArray\, detached from the current graph.

name: ndarray.expand_dims
description: Adds an additional dimension to the current array without altering any data.

name: ndarray.flatten
description: Flatten this array without altering any data.

name: ndarray.grad
description: Returns gradient buffer attached to this NDArray.

name: ndarray.ndim
description: Returns the number of dimensions of this array

name: ndarray.reshape
description: Returns a view of this array with a new shape without altering any data.

name: ndarray.size
description: Number of elements in the array.

name: ndarray.slice_assign
description: Assign the rhs to a cropped subset of this NDarray in place. Returns the view of this NDArray.

name: ndarray.slice_assign_scalar
description: Assign the scalar to a cropped subset of this NDArray. Value will broadcast to the shape of the cropped shape and will be cast to the same dtype of the NDArray.

name: ndarray.squeeze
description: Remove dimensions with size 1 from this array without altering any data.

name: ndarray.to_dlpack_for_read
description: Returns a reference view of NDArray that represents as DLManagedTensor until all previous write operations on the current array are finished.

name: ndarray.to_dlpack_for_write
description: Returns a reference view of NDArray that represents as DLManagedTensor until all previous read/write operations on the current array are finished.

name: ndarray.tostype
description: Return a copy of the array with chosen storage type.

name: ndarray.wait_to_read
description: Waits until all previous write operations on the current array are finished.
